---
title: Crispy Chicken Tacos with Tomato Salad
description: These tacos are a double whammy! We can’t decide what we like more, the crispy bites of cornflake-crusted chicken, or the incredible lime crema you’re going to create yourself. Thank goodness that in these warming tortillas, we don’t have to choose!
